Theme class

Source: R/class_Theme.R
Theme.Rd

Theme class

Theme class

Details

Definition for the Theme class. This is a parent class that contains shared fields and methods for the SingleTheme and MultiTheme classes.

This method intentionally throws an error.

See also

new_single_theme(), new_multi_theme().

Public fields

id

character value.

name

character value.

feature

list of Feature objects.
